subject: Women's British Open (Golf)
Golf
lead_paragraph: Playing 36 holes on a day that ran the gamut of seasons, Jiyai Shin posted scores of 71-73 to finish at nine under par at the Women’s British Open, nine strokes ahead of her fellow South Korean Inbee Park.
